<li data-start="3562" data-end="3631">
<p data-start="3564" data-end="3631">Turning them into evaluative criteria for systems or institutions</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3632" data-end="3720" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="3634" data-end="3720" data-is-last-node="">Or stress-testing where your intuitions diverge most sharply from Ammann’s assumptions</p>
</li>
