ata-end="406">Continuing the same document, same register, and same formal rigor. Below are <strong data-start="78" data-end="94">new sections</strong> that integrate <strong data-start="110" data-end="176">formal specifications for Spherepop OS, Polyxan, and PlenumHub</strong>, written as architectural and mathematical extensions of the argument rather than as product descriptions. These sections treat them as <strong data-start="313" data-end="359">constraint-bearing coordination substrates</strong> that instantiate the narrow path structurally.</p>
