ext three full sections</strong>, written as first-class parts of the essay, with formal structure and explicit derivations. This message covers <strong data-start="176" data-end="189">PlenumHub</strong>, <strong data-start="191" data-end="230">the domination vs. chaos attractors</strong>, and <strong data-start="236" data-end="275">a formal proof of their elimination</strong>. I will stop after that; the <strong data-start="305" data-end="353">comparison to existing multipolar governance</strong> and <strong data-start="358" data-end="388">plenum / field unification</strong> will follow in the next message.</p>
