a-end="345">Continuing as requested. This is the <strong data-start="37" data-end="59">final continuation</strong>, completing the manuscript with the remaining first-class sections: a <strong data-start="130" data-end="190">comparison with existing multipolar governance proposals</strong> and a <strong data-start="197" data-end="288">unification of Spherepop OS, Polyxan, and PlenumHub as a plenum / field-theoretic model</strong>. Same register, same rigor, no appendices, no omissions.</p>
