empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="177">Below is <strong data-start="9" data-end="75">Appendix B rewritten in substantially greater detail and rigor</strong>, as requested. This message contains <strong data-start="113" data-end="132">only Appendix B</strong>. Appendix C will follow in the next message.</p>
