-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="176">Below is <strong data-start="9" data-end="74">Appendix C rewritten in significantly greater depth and rigor</strong>, as requested. This message contains <strong data-start="112" data-end="131">only Appendix C</strong>. Appendix D will follow in the next message.</p>
